lor": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1888553119216035519"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIlbSyrMvt/MxOEAMaCTExNDE5NTE2MiCHjJO/BjAAOHVAGXITMTg4ODU1MzExOTIxNjAzNTUxOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1743131033.624611", "card_id": "Q_1886365701876466619", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 146}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "辅导孩子作业，能想到的方法都用了，怎么教都不会，反而更差了，又新增不爱说话的习惯，到底是哪出了问题？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我家大姑娘现在小学三年级，基本上中午和晚上都要辅导作业，尤其是晚上，常常要熬到 10 点，甚至 11 点。即便如此，孩子白天在学校学过的知识，晚上辅导过的题目，第二天又全忘了，感觉就像在做无用功，白忙活一场。每次都是耐心地重复讲解，忍不住的时候骂过、甚至打过，这些方法都没用，反而情况更糟了。现在孩子变得不爱说话，你问她十句，她最多只答两句，声音还特别小。看着孩子这样，我和孩子妈妈真是崩溃到不行，孩子妈妈开始怀疑是不是孩子脑子或者基因有问题，甚至想去医院做检查。因为这件事，我们夫妻俩争吵过好多次，内心满是无奈、痛苦、煎熬，真不知道到底出了什么问题，真心希望能得到知友的帮助，到底怎么做？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9db9df5f6d5e335ba6c285220f27cf16_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1886365701876466619"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIlbSyrMvt/MxOEAMaCTExNDA5MjcyMiDWofO+BjAAOMoBQBpyEzE4ODYzNjU3MDE4NzY0NjY2MTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1743131033.625297", "card_id": "Q_452000285", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 944}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小学二年级数学老师，要求学生写 ÷ 时，必须横线尺子比着写、两个点特别圆，是不是有点过分？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-0843f71e539b329bb474de4c076ab9c6_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/452000285"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlbSyrMvt/MxOEAMaCDYyNzIzODIzINasioMGMAA4vg5AG3IJNDUyMDAwMjg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"